                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                               Theodore R. Sizer, <em>The Autobiography of Colonel John Trumbull, Patriot-Artist, 1746-1843</em>, Yale University Press (U.S.) (New Haven, CT, 1953)
                                            </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Wadsworth Atheneum Museum of Art, <em>John Trumbull, Painter-Patriot: An Exhibition Organized to Honor the Bicentennial of the Artist's Birth</em>, exh. cat., Wadsworth Atheneum Museum of Art (Hartford, CT, 1956), p. 11, ill.
                             </p>
