                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Kenyon Castle Bolton, III, Peter G. Huenink, Earl A. Powell III, Harry Z. Rand, and Nanette C. Sexton, <em>American Art at Harvard</em>, exh. cat., Fogg Art Museum (Cambridge, MA, 1972), cat. 20, ill.
                             </p>
