                                              Ethan Lasser, ed., <em>The Philosophy Chamber: Art and Science in Harvard’s Teaching Cabinet, 1766–1820</em>, exh. cat., Harvard Art Museums (Cambridge, MA, 2017), p. 108, Plate 44; ; p. 262 in Andrew Gelfand's "Chronology"
